  "text": "Remark III.4 Another method considering dynamic invariant sets for distributed systems was recently proposed in [CITATION_1] . However, while the dynamics in [CITATION_2] are stateindependent, the dynamics presented in this paper depend on the current state of the system and can therefore adapt to specific scenarios.",
